px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">The impact of the COVID-19 pande=
mic on third party food delivery is a Rorschach test. What you see depends =
on what you believe.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Some view third party food delivery operat=
ors, such as DoorDash, UberEats, and Grubhub, as heroes of the pandemic, a =
