ides business lags.&nbsp;DoorDash is not far behind, with a market capitali=
zation around $60B following a successful mid-pandemic IPO, earlier this we=
ek they bought a <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMuOgzAMRb=
