2R2EafCP-kfJV6cIg" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">ag=
ainst their will</a>.&nbsp;Nonetheless, they were successful in growing the=
 new market by unlocking new supply and opening up new geographies.&nbsp;</=
p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 1em 0;">At the same time, they executed a low end disruption to take exi=
sting market share away from Grubhub.&nbsp;By leveraging independent contra=
ctors rather than restaurant employees, they pitched a lower cost of delive=
ry to restaurants. This was achieved by sharing delivery workers between re=
staurants, paying <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUcGurCAM_=
