t, and third party delivery operators do not care.</p><p style=3D"color: #1=
a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">How could th=
ird party delivery kill your business while bringing customers in the door?=
&nbsp;The model below shows a P&amp;L for a restaurant that does ~$1M in sa=
les annually at a 15% EBITDA margin, this would be considered very good by =
any standards.&nbsp;As you can see at the top, as third party delivery take=
